description:
Our Seasons - The Circle of Life | Nature Documentary 

Watch 'Birds of Passage - A Secret Journey Through the Skies' here: https://youtu.be/qNcEmhqSobY

Our seasons shape the cycle of life in dramatic ways. Spring, summer, autumn, or winter – every season is unique, each presenting nature with new challenges. The constant change in living conditions demands extraordinary feats from animals and plants throughout the year. And the survival strategies of the squirrel, fox, and many others could hardly be more fascinating. 

The film takes us on a breathtaking journey of discovery through indigenous nature. After the privations of winter, life explodes in spring, and the summer heat is followed by the autumn harvest season. Extraordinary animal stories – some humorous, some dramatic, but always with an eye to the season’s special features – bring the magic of our seasons to life.

Enjoy stories about nature, wildlife, culture, people, history and more to come.
